kate park's home page june 2000 hi my name is kate park i m a first grader at laurel school in atherton california my favorite things are maple syrup lollipops drawing and painting and jewelry making i once had a boyfriend at preschool who kept saying kate is the most beautiful girl in the world but we couldn t go to the same elementary school my daddy and mommy love traveling and i ve joined them since i impressed them by carrying my diapers and milk bottles in my own backpack when i was one and a half i have already made more than thirty international flights and here are some of my travel pictures
